version_description:
Minor bug fix for iOS 9.
Minor UX refinements.
Minor changes in UI.
Bug fixes and feature enhancements.
In comparison to 1.9.0, this version has few minor bug fixes and locales.
Improved App Notification handling.
Improved notifications handling.
Incremental small bug fixes in 3.06v.
Elaborated explanation texts about managed apps on the app list page.
Update with google login screen to work well with iOS 11.0.

Admins can now request apps to be managed. Once the user agrees, admins will have additional controls over these apps. There is no change to unmanaged apps and admins do not need to make any apps managed.

We've also released a new feedback page.
Fixed erroneous display and handling of notifications that say "Couldn't automatically sync 'Google Device Policy'. Tap here to sync the device yourself."
Elaborated explanation texts about managed apps on the app list page.
Bug fix in the flow which enforces managed apps on app list page.
Elaborated explanation texts about managed apps on the app list page.

Improved user messages in some error cases.
Bug fixes.
Fixed a bug that the app sometimes fails to make progress at "App connection" page.
Incremental small bug fixes in 3.06v.
Revamped Welcome Screens. Bug fixes
Bug fixes in Welcome Screen.
Cosmetic bug fixes in text and text alignments.

* Minimum iOS version supported is updated to 10.
* Minor UI update to support landscape mode in welcome screens on iPad.

* Handles notifications more reliably.
* Shows localized app genre.
New UI for user sign-in and app list page.
Nutrition Labels and minor bug fixes.
